<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比只找到了玛莎阿姨购物清单上的一样东西：番茄汤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿着它去了结账柜台。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>基弗先生隔着厚厚的眼镜片儿盯着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比试着微笑，但他是一个害羞的男孩儿，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他觉得很不自在。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简是这几个孩子里面最外向的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她总是微笑着和每个人交谈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比注意到了结账柜台上一只泰迪熊身上系着的彩色气球。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个气球多少钱？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60098</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆特别喜欢玩儿气球，所以鲍比想给他买一个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60099</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“二十五美分。”基弗先生回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要两个。”鲍比一边说一边数钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74057</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不觉得这个对你来说有点幼稚了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74058</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨在鲍比身后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是给我的。”鲍比咯咯笑，“给兰姆的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨奇怪地看了看鲍比。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91863</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给小婴……”鲍比开口时，还没意识到兰姆已经不存在了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，没事。我不想买了。”他迅速说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110070</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不知道为什么，鲍比突然有点儿想哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110071</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不想要个糖吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>基弗先生递来了一个装满彩色糖果的罐子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比谨慎地选了一个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“继续拿吧。”基弗先生说，“多拿一点儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131333</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>以前鲍比不得不和他的兄弟姐妹分享一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131334</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在他是一个人了，所以他可以享受更多的一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137611</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比开心地抓了满满一把糖果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨因为鲍比没有在购物中帮更多的忙而感到生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，她还是给他做了最喜欢的三明治之后，才出门去见她的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然鲍比很喜欢花生黄油配腌黄瓜三明治，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但一个人吃，一点儿意思都没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>周围安静的让他感到悲伤，所以他出门了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180548</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他捡起一个足球，但没人和他一起玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180549</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他骑上自行车，但一个人骑车也没意思。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抬头看看阳光灿烂的天空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有多久太阳才会落山啊？”他想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一天似乎比以往任何时候都要长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比努力地去想他的兄弟姐妹们曾对他做过的一切坏事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208154</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他努力装作一点儿也不思念他的兄弟姐妹的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赛伊总是戏弄我。”他大声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“简总是尖叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟一直都喜欢发号施令。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆一天到晚地哭。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但事实上，他非常想念他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，一个可怕的想法闯进了他的脑袋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>要是他再也见不到赛伊、潘瑟、简和兰姆了怎么办？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比的心开始砰砰跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果休伊走了，我的愿望永远不会消失了怎么办？”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他怕极了，怕得说不出话来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比用最快的速度穿过了森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑到了休伊的井边，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后试着将那个木桶从井底拉上来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“休伊！休伊！我改变主意了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比大叫着用尽全力去拉那个木桶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不知为什么，那个木桶在井底一动不动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不！不！”鲍比大叫着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301744</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但绳子依然纹丝不动，木桶静静地停留在井底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比跌坐在地上大哭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他怕得要死，又觉得非常孤单。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>321184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他精疲力尽地闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>321185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比再次睁开眼睛的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他过了好一会儿才想起自己在哪里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一定是在休伊的井边睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>333349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鲍比？”远处传来了一个熟悉的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343129</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比的心怦怦直跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345671</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他知道那个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>352456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊、潘瑟和简从树后面向他跑来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>352457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355334</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比忍不住哭了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>360320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真的非常非常抱歉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>360321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>365033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他大哭着去拥抱他的兄弟姐妹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>365034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>370041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们奇怪地看着他，但却一句话都没说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>370042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>371999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>太阳落山了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>372000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>377487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比再次见到家人后，实在是太开心了，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>377488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>383157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几乎压抑不住自己的快乐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>